        {
            "title": "警聯入境處荃灣掃黃 9內地女涉違反逗留條件被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/43880db27fe91ccf87e53b09857ff41d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250312/_2025031223031170996.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>荃灣警區特別職務隊聯同入境事務處，根據線報及經深入調查後，今日（12日）展開代號「嶺馬」的掃黃行動。行動中，人員在川龍街及沙咀道一帶拘捕9名年齡介乎27至38歲的內地女子，涉嫌「違反逗留條件」。被捕女子正被扣留調查，稍後將交由相關部門跟進。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133855/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方拘捕9名年齡介乎27至38歲的內地女子。警方提供\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/398b0806e908811e243c690386805cc7/2025-03/MIU_anti-vice_SDS_2_TWDIST.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方拘捕9名年齡介乎27至38歲的內地女子。警方提供\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057809/即時-港聞-警聯入境處荃灣掃黃-9內地女涉違反逗留條件被捕",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-12 23:31:50",
